Package com.bewsoftware.utils

Class AvlTree<E extends Comparable<E>>

java.lang.Object
com.bewsoftware.utils.AvlTree<E>
Type Parameters:
E - type of item stored in this tree.
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<E>, Collection<E>, Set<E>
public final class AvlTree<E extends Comparable<E>> extends Object implements Set<E>
This is a Binary Search Tree with the default capability of being a Balanced Binary Search Tree.

This class does not support storage of either nulls or duplicates.

Since:
1.0.9
Version:
2.1.0
Author:
Bradley Willcott
